OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRebellious Andean bear     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsneaks out of US zoo -     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ftwice                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New security measures added to this    
OL,6, Andean bear's habitat by the Saint     
OL,7, Louis Zoo were no match for his        
OL,8, adventurous nature.                    
OL,10,FAfter escaping his habitat earlier this
OL,11,Fmonth, on 7 February, the four-year-old
OL,12,Fbear, named Ben, snuck out again on    
OL,13,FThursday afternoon.                    
OL,15,FAndean bears are only found in South   
OL,16,FAmerica, but are vulnerable due to     
OL,17,Fhabitat loss and poaching threats.     
OL,19,FBen is now back at the zoo after       
OL,20,Froaming free for 50 minutes.           
